_MPC_e17500.long_name: Marginal propensity to consume medical expenses
_MPC_e17500.description: Defined as dollar change in medical-expense consumption divided by dollar change in income.  Typical value is in [0,1] range.

_MPC_e18400.long_name: Marginal propensity to consume state-and-local taxes
_MPC_e18400.description: Defined as dollar change in state-and-local-taxes consumption divided by dollar change in income.  Typical value is in [0,1] range.

_MPC_e19800.long_name: Marginal propensity to consume charity cash contributions
_MPC_e19800.description: Defined as dollar change in charity-cash-contribution consumption divided by dollar change in income.  Typical value is in [0,1] range.

_MPC_e20400.long_name: Marginal propensity to consume miscellaneous deduction expenses
_MPC_e20400.description: Defined as dollar change in miscellaneous-deduction-expense consumption divided by dollar change in income.  Typical value is in [0,1] range.
